---
import Page from "@layouts/Page.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "consts";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import myPhoto from "@assets/images/casual-photo.jpg";
import RectPattern from "@components/RectPattern.astro";
import MyName from "@components/MyName.astro";
import ContactIcons from "@components/ContactIcons.astro";
---

<Page metaTitle={"About - " + SITE_TITLE} metaDescription={SITE_DESCRIPTION} transition:animate="slide">
  <div class="name mt-12 sm:mt-0">
    <small class="uppercase">About</small>
    <h2>
      <MyName />
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="flex max-sm:block mt-8 gap-4">
    <div class="flex-1 sm:pr-2">
      <p class="sm:text-justify">
        Hi there! I'm excited to introduce myself. I'm Lasitha Prabodha Weligampola. I discovered my passion for
        technology back in 2002 when I started playing around with computers. Now, as a Frontend Engineer with over 7
        years of experience, I create web and mobile applications that are both functional and enjoyable to use. ‚ú®
      </p>
      <p class="sm:text-justify">
        My expertise lies in Angular, React, TypeScript, C#, .NET Core, and various other web technologies. I've worked
        with startups, medium-sized, and large-scale companies, leading the development of cutting-edge applications and
        revitalizing legacy systems.
      </p>
      <p class="sm:text-justify">
        Coding keeps my brain buzzing, but fire up some metal and that's when I truly come alive. üôÇ‚Äç‚ÜïÔ∏èü§òüèº The energy just
        hits different. Whether it's Black Sabbath, Gojira, Tool or Metallica, I enjoy them all. üé∏
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="details-photo h-min relative">
      <Image format="avif" src={myPhoto} loading="eager" alt="Lasitha Prabodha Weligampola" width={300} height={300} />
      <RectPattern width={320} height={320} />
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="sm:text-justify">
    Continuous learning and improvement are essential to me, whether it's mastering new technologies or enhancing user
    interfaces for better usability. While I highly value the power of teamwork and fostering strong relationships, I'm
    equally capable of working effectively in both independent and collaborative environments.
  </p>
  <p class="sm:text-justify">
    As I embark on the next chapter, I'm excited to push boundaries in technology, and make a positive impact.  <span class="sm:block"><a class="link" href="/contact">Let's
    connect</a> and discuss tech, your favourite metal band, or collaboration opportunities! ü§ùüèº</span> 
  </p>

  <ContactIcons showEmail={true} />
</Page>

<style>
  :global(.details-photo > svg) {
    position: absolute;
    left: 10px;
    top: 10px;
    z-index: -1;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .details-photo {
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .details-photo:hover {
    transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
  }

  .details-photo:hover img {
    filter: none;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  :global(.details-photo:hover > svg) {
    transform: translate(6px, 6px);
  }

  img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    position: relative;
    background-image: url("/src/assets/images/blur.png");
    background-size: contain;
    filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .details {
      display: block;
    }

    img {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .details-photo:hover {
      transform: translate(0px, -5px);
    }
    p{
      
    }
  }
</style>
